properties.name: aquasecurity:trivy:Labels:description
properties.value: The Universal Base Image Minimal is a stripped down image that uses microdnf as a package manager. This base image is freely redistributable, but Red Soft only supports Red Soft technologies through subscriptions for Red Soft products. This image is maintained by Red Soft and updated regularly.

properties.name: aquasecurity:trivy:Labels:summary
properties.value: Provides release of the minimal Red OS Universal Base Image
